OL,10,GPoet and activist Muriel Rukseyer said
OL,11,G"The universe is made of stories not
OL,12,Gatoms". Some animal communication
OL,13,Gcould be described as storytelling,
OL,14,Gcrows maintain intergenerational
OL,15,Ggrudges , elephants mourn their dead,
OL,16,Gand seek revenge, and orcas wear dead
OL,17,Gsalmon as hats, but as far as we
OL,18,Gunderstand, we're the only animals who
OL,19,Guse allegory and metaphor, myth and
OL,20,Gimagination. Award-winning author
